title: Born to renovate: The house where Bruce Springsteen wrote Born to Run goes on sale
text: Born to renovate: The house where Bruce Springsteen wrote Born to Run goes on sale Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (14 minutes ago) Sellers hope the new owners will preserve ‘the Bruce factor’ in the two-bedroom house in Long Branch, New Jersey It’s not exactly a mansion of glory, but at least the traffic outside doesn’t look bad – there appear to be no signs of the highway being jammed with broken heroes on a last-chance powerdrive.
